1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 51-07 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to requiring vendors to provide physical copies of tickets upon request.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 51-07 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Event tickets - Physical copies.
7 If an individual purchases a ticket required for admission to an event and the vendor
8 provides the ticket to the individual in digital format, the individual may request a physical copy
9 of the ticket, which must be provided by the vendor at no charge, except the vendor may charge
10 up to ten dollars in shipping and handling fees.
